name: A Touch That Breathes Life
description:
From the 100 Days of Drawing Series //

This 2021 personal challenge started in early March. The goal, to produce a finished piece, everyday, for 100 days  //

"The thumbs lightly touched but their inaudible sound waves propagated generating a sphere of light and life. Small things matter. Matter is small things." 

3000x3000 JPG
